 the first time, the detection performance on three classes surpasses\n80 APH (L2) simultaneously. Code will be available at\n\\url{https://github.com/sankin97/LoGoNet}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 02:00:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 13:15:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
