 of\n$O(\\epsilon^{-3})$. This manuscript commemorates the mathematician Boris Polyak\n(1935 -2023).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 14:55:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
